OL,3,C"Loving, caring and generous man"
OL,4,Ckilled in Nottingham shooting
OL,6,FThe family of a man killed in a
OL,7,Fshooting in Nottingham have described
OL,8,Fhim as "loving, caring and generous",
OL,9,Fand say they'll always remember him.
OL,11,FCoel Tainton was found dead at a
OL,12,Fproperty in Ryeland Gardens in The
OL,13,FMeadows just after 5.30am on Saturday
OL,14,FFebruary 28.
OL,16,FHis family has now paid tribute to the
OL,17,F24-year-old, who they described as a
OL,18,F"beloved son, brother, nephew, cousin,
OL,19,Fgrandson, and friend to so many".
OL,21,F"A precious soul"
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/4
