FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1772629886
OL,3,C"Loving, caring and generous man"
OL,4,Ckilled in Nottingham shooting
OL,6,FA statement by the family released
OL,7,Fthrough Nottinghamshire Police said:
OL,8,F"Coel was loving, caring, and fiercely
OL,9,Fprotective of those he held close. His
OL,10,Fheart was big, generous, and full of
OL,11,Fkindness.
OL,13,F"He had a precious soul and a
OL,14,Fcontagious laugh that could light up
OL,15,Fany room and touch everyone around him.
OL,17,F"He brought joy, warmth, and comfort
OL,18,Fto our lives in countless ways. His
OL,19,Fhumour, strength, and endless love
OL,20,Fwill forever remain in our hearts.
OL,26,@pD@AOUuD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/4
