OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1772629886
OL,3,C"Loving, caring and generous man"
OL,4,Ckilled in Nottingham shooting
OL,6,F"Though words cannot express the depth
OL,7,Fof our loss, we know his love
OL,8,Fsurrounds us still. He will be so
OL,9,Fsadly missed, deeply cherished, and
OL,10,Floved forever."
OL,12,FPolice said a murder investigation was
OL,13,Flaunched following the discovery.
OL,15,FJack Preston, 34, was charged with
OL,16,Fmurder, assault by beating of an
OL,17,Femergency worker and a public order
OL,18,Foffence on Tuesday, March 3.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@OO]
