OL,4,Ckilled in Nottingham shooting
OL,6,FPreston of Ryeland Gardens was
OL,7,Fremanded in custody and is due to
OL,8,Fappear at Nottingham Magistrates'
OL,9,FCourt on Wednesday, March 4.
